  "text": "The coercivity property (15) is the key estimate. Note that, as in [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , we rely on the numerical computations of some integrals to prove it. In pratice, the function g is chosen as the unique Schwartz solution of the equation (other choices are certainly possible)",
